          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"co-cr-fe-ni-gibbs-free-energy-explorer\">Co-Cr-Fe-Ni Gibbs Free Energy Explorer</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Interactive <strong>marimo</strong> notebook for Gibbs-energy CSV files named <code>Gibbs_&lt;T&gt;K.csv</code>.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Required CSV columns: <code>Co</code>, <code>Cr</code>, <code>Fe</code>, <code>Ni</code>, <code>G_LIQ</code>, <code>G_FCC</code>.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Stable phase condition:</span>\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||[G_{stable} = \\min(G_{LIQ}, G_{FCC})||]</marimo-tex></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
